Subject objects can act as an Observer or as an Observable, it extends Observable calss an implements Observer interface.

Subjects can be used as a bridge when convwerting projects from impperative programing to reactive.

Types : 

	- Async Subject : Only emits last value of Observable

	- Behavior Subject : Emits the most reccently emitted item and all the subsequent items (emited later) of the source Observable

	- Publish Subject : Emits all the subsequent items of the source Observable at the time of subscription

	- Replay Subject : Emits all the items of the source Observable regardless of when the subscriber subscribes

